INSERT INTO `article_details` VALUES (99, 36, 'en', 'how_it_works', 'How it works', '<h2>How To Play Euromillions Online</h2>\r\n<p>Because of it''s now worldwide popularity, Euromillions has quickly become one of the largest lottery games in the world. Excitement among it''s players reaches fever pitch, with rollover jackpots having people queuing up to buy their ticket. Previously, this game could be played only by those people who resided in one of the aforementioned participating countries. They would visited retail lottery outlets to buy Euro Millions tickets. Today, the tickets have been made available online. Thanks to online ticket purchasing agencies that buy your tickets for you, you can now play Euromillions online from anywhere in the world</p>\r\n</br>\r\n<h2>Addtional Resources</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://euromillions.com/how-to-play-euromillions-online">Learn how we do it</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://euromillions.com/test">About us</a></p>\r\n</br>', 'How to play Euromillions', 'Euromillions, Euro Millions guide, tutorial, infographic', 'Learn how to play Euromillions Online', 1, 1353324425, 2, 'Admin Istrator', 'how-to-play', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1353324263, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `article_details` VALUES (100, 37, 'en', 'faq', 'FAQ', '<h1><a name="qgroup7">How to play</a> </h1></br></br>\r\n<h2><a>How can I play?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You can play from any location worldwide. Please click on the “<a href="http://euromillions.com">Play now</a>” link and follow the instructions. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a >How can I play the same numbers again?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are feeling lucky and would like to play the same numbers again, go to your ticket history page under “My account”; you can see your previous tickets and to replay the same numbers again simply click on the “Play Again” button. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a>When is the next draw and how can I find out the results?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Please click on <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/en/euromillions-lottery" rel="nofollow">Euromillions lottery</a> to find out when the next draw is. We usually send email notifications of the results. Please make sure you have marked a tick for receiving emails, newsletters and notifications from Euromillions.com. You also can check the results by clicking the following link <a href="http://euromillions.com/euromillions-results">Euromillions results</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a >What is the cut-off time for buying a ticket to have it included in my current week’s drawings?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You can see the cut-off time in Summary under “My Account” option. The usual cut-off time is every Friday at 19:00 CET. Running out of time!! Click <a href="http://euromillions.com/">here to play now</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a >How and when does the winner get paid?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We pay into the winner’s Euromillions.com account immediately after the results have been announced. The winner cannot withdraw the winnings for four weeks if the winning amount is more than one thousand Euros (1.000,00 €), due to the Euromillions cashout policy. As an acting agent it is Euromillions.com’s responsibility to collect winnings on behalf of winners and to transfer directly to their Euromillions.com account. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a >How do I get notifications of my winnings or losses?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide our customers with an email notification service to inform them about results. So please make sure we have your correct email address in your account details. To check your email address please <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/en/account/settings" rel="nofollow">click here </a> and make sure you have marked the option “Send me Euromillions lottery results every Friday after the draw” option under your account settings. </p>\r\n</br><h1><a name="qgroup4">Payouts</a> </h1></br></br>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_18">How do I withdraw my winnings from my Euromillions.com playing account?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Once your winnings are confirmed you can withdraw them by transferring them from your Euromillions.com account to your personal bank account or credit card account. To withdraw your funds, click <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/en/account/withdraw">here</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_19">What is the minimum and maximum withdrawal limits?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The minimum withdrawal limit is 25,00 €. There is no maximum withdrawal limit but players are required to wait for four weeks for any withdrawals more than 1.000,00 €. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_20">Does the withdrawal beneficiary’s name need to be the same as the name I used to buy the ticket?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, the name of withdrawal beneficiary and the name of the payee of the ticket must match due to our Anti-money-laundering policy. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_21">How can I transfer the winnings/gains to my bank account?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Once your winnings or gains are confirmed they are automatically credited to your “My Euromillions.com” account. You can then either transfer it to your registered bank account/credit card account or you can use it to purchase more tickets. \r\nIt is your responsibility to make sure you comply with the following to transfer your winnings into your personal bank account: </p>\r\n\r\n<p>All the methods of payment must be verified prior to withdrawal. Click <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/en/account/verify-credit-card/">here</a> to verify.\r\nThe details of the beneficiary of the withdrawal must match the details of the payee who funded the account.</li>\r\n<p>We only pay out winnings. The value of any awards or bonuses cannot be paid out but can only be redeemed against buying more tickets.</p>\r\n</br><h1><a name="qgroup5">Security and privacy</a> </h1></br></br>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_22">Is my personal data and credit card information secure?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It is our responsibility and priority to make sure all information and details provided by our customers are dealt with high confidentiality and stored using a secure method. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_23">Does Euromillions.com disclose my data to any third party or person?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Under no circumstances will Euromillions.com disclose a customer’s confidential information to any third party or person unless it is required for legal purposes. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_24">How secure are my details?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We always use a secure server system to exchange information to ensure all transactions are handled with the highest security. </p>\r\n\r\n</br><h1><a name="qgroup7">Legal information</a> </h1></br></br>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_29">Do I need to pay tax on my gains or winnings?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All winnings are 100 percent tax free. But we always advise that you consult your local tax office to find out more about tax regulations. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_30">Can Euromillions.com handle my tax related issues?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Euromillions.com does not advise any of its customers on tax regulations. Please consult your local tax office. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name="question_31">What is your anti-money-laundering policy?</a> </h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our anti-money-laundering policy restricts customers to using the same beneficiary name for the withdrawal that they initially used for the payment. In simple words the name of the withdrawal beneficiary must match the name of the payer of the ticket. </p>', 'Frequently asked questions', 'FAQ  Euromillions, Euromillions Questions,', 'Frequently asked questions about Euromillions', 1, 1353582048, 2, 'Admin Istrator', 'FAQs', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1353408731, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
