INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (1, 1, 'en', 'record_euromillions_jackpot_is_won_by_a_french_player', 'Record EuroMillions jackpot is won by a French player', '<p>9, 28, 30, 32 and 49 and the Lucky Stars 9 and 10 were the life changing magic numbers and the second largest single ticket prize in the draws history. 6 other ticket holders who matched all 5 numbers and 1 Lucky Star each bagged a tasty €372,000,000. The EuroMillions jackpot is now back down to a minimum of €15 million, will the rollover madness continue or will someone strike it rich this Friday?</p>', 'Record EuroMillions jackpot is won by a French player', 'record jackpot, euromillions, euromillions jackpot, french euromillions winner', 'Second largest Euromillions Jackpot won by a French ticket holder', 2, 1319800081, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'winning frenchman 2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1316032743, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (2, 2, 'en', 'wheres_the_record_euromillions_winning_frenchman', 'Where''s the record EuroMillions winning Frenchman?', '<p>The whole of France is searching for the record jackpot winner. All that''s known so far is that the winning ticket was bought somewhere in Normandy and GBP142 Million are waiting to be collected. Rumours have it the ticket was purchased from a small betting kiosk in a pub somewhere near Pont-l''Eveque in the region of Deauville, this is according to the bar owner a Mr Roberto Gnocchi. The truth is not yet known, maybe the ticket has been lost or lying around some lucky persons house forgotten for now. If collected it will propel the winner to 250th in France''s rich list. Check out if you have the <a href="/euromillions-results">euromillions lucky numbers tonight</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<a href="/lottery-news/record-euromillions-jackpot-won-by-french-player">Record Euromillions jackpot won by French person</a>', 'Where''s the record EuroMillions winning Frenchman?', 'Euromillions winner frenchman, France euromillions winner, euromillions winner', 'The record winning Frenchman still has to claim his Euromillions jackpot. Who is it?', 2, 1319800066, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'winning frenchman 1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1316711340, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (3, 3, 'en', 'britain_once_again_boasts_a_euromillions_winner', 'Britain once again boasts a Euromillions winner', '<p>The Euromillions lottery will once again transform the life of a lucky Briton. Camelot have officially revealed that the £101 million jackpot has been claimed by a someone in Britian. The winner has yet to make their name public at this time, leaving us in the dark as to whether there is even one individual winner or a syndicate. One thing for certain however, is that the 3rd biggest jackpot in Euromillions history will be in the hands of somebody in Britain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winning numbers drawn on Friday night were 18, 26, 34, 38, 42 and lucky stars 5 and 8. Shortly after the drawing on Friday the winner phoned Camelot to confirm their win.. The cheque is expected to be handed over early this Monday morning when Camelot representatives meet to validate the claim.</p>  \r\n\r\n<p>A spokeswoman for the National Lottery is quoted saying “This is amazing news - we are absolutely delighted for the winner.". The Euromillions has not only created some of the richest people in the UK but is also known for contributing to the £30million raised by the National Lottery  every week for causes based in the UK.  Lottery chiefs claim ticket demand peaked in the last 2 hours before the draw, as people rushed to get a last minute shot at the £101million. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Euromillions history in the UK is that of some of the largest payouts in the game. Earlier in 2011 a Scottish couple Colin and Christine Weir won the highest ever Euromillions jackpot of £161 million. Their win bought homes and driving lessons for their children Jamie 22 and Carly 24, and in a show of great modesty Mr Weird boasted keeping his ''reliable'' old Suzuki SX4 and Suzuki Ignis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Second to the Weirs is another UK denizen, who chose to remain anonymous with their £113 million win last October. Our winner from this Friday makes the third largest Euromillions payout in the UK. The fourth biggest winner with £84 million was in May. Just a few months previous in February 2010 £56 million was won by Nigel Page and Justine Laycock of Gloucestershire putting them in fifth. The sixth biggest payout of £45 million was made in November 2009 to Les and Sam Scadding of South Wales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many now wait with bated breath to see if the now 703rd  richest person in the UK will reveal themselves. Have we multiple winners in a syndicate? Or another happy couple? Will we ever know for sure or will they remain anonymous to avoid the infamy involved with such a huge lottery win?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next draw will be this Tuesday 11th October and the estimated jackpot is £13 million. Don''t forget you can get your ticket online here today, and even see the Euromillions results on our site. Watch this space for more updates and Euromillions news.</p>', 'Britain once again boasts a Euromillions winner', 'Euromillions winner, Euromillions british winner, British lottery winner', 'Once again a Brittish person has won the Euromillions lottery taking home the massive jackpot of £101 million', 2, 1319537418, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'britain-once-again-boasts-a-euromillions-winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1318168391, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (4, 4, 'en', 'latest_euromillionaires_speak_publicly', 'Latest Euromillionaires Speak Publicly', '<p>Since a single UK ticket holder came forward to claim Friday''s  €101,203,600.70 jackpot, the question on everyone''s mind is “Who has won such a massive amount of money”. At Euromillions.com we can proudly announce the winners to be Dave and Angela Dawes of Wisbech, Cambridgeshire. Dave (47) and Angela (43) have spoken at a press conference on the Tuesday afternoon and have much to say on the subject.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple have been together 4 years and currently live in a 1 bedroom apartment at £70 per week. Despite not being married Angela took Dave''s surname after divorcing her former husband and meeting Dave. Angela told a press conference “We couldn''t afford to get married and decided, as we were going to get married in the future, I would change my name to his anyway”. Of course with their financial situation now radically different they plan to buy a new homes in Chelsea and abroad and get married next year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dave who is an avid fan of Chealsea Football Club plans to buy his season ticket, adding: “I''m not worried about getting a private box -I want to stand with the real fans to watch my team play”. A down to earth point of view to take but also half jokes “I''d also love to live near the ground and have Frank Lampard come over for a cup of tea”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple have made their generosity clear and vow “We have a list of 15 to 20 people who we are gong to make millionaires. Anyone who has helped us through our life”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple were watching the draw together live as the numbers came up, “We were watching TV and the Euromillions draw show came on so we kept watching, not thinking we would win anything”. It was Dave''s ticket that won the jackpot and he had this to say: “We got our tickets out and watched in shock as, one by one, the numbers came up on the line I''d chosen”, “We couldn''t believe it! It was too late to call Camelot so I kept the ticket on me all night until the morning but we didn''t sleep a wink”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The jackpot win puts the couple 1million Euros ahead of pop-star David Bowie in the world''s rich list and are naturally delighted at their win and how it will change their lives and the lives of their loved ones. We at Euromillions.com wish them the best of luck in the future with their winnings.</p>', 'Latest Euromillionaires Speak Publicly', 'latest euromillions winners, Dave Dawes, Angela Dawes, Euromillions winner', 'Latest Euromillions winners from Britain goes public, read more about the winners at Euromillions.com', 2, 1319537547, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Latest Euromillionaires Speak Publicly', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1318341732, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (5, 5, 'en', 'french_euromillions_winner_collect_winnings', 'French Euromillions Winner Collect Winnings', '<p>After a full month waiting the French winner of a massive €162million has finally come forward to collect his cheque. If you recall exactly 30 days ago the second biggest jackpot win was confirmed to belong to someone in France, however with nobody stepping forward the French press had gone into a frenzy in their attempts to track the winner down.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Euromillions.com we are delighted to announce that the French man has come forward and collected his winnings from Française des jeux  on the 13th October. The winner has chosen to remain anonymous but we can reveal him to be of the Calvados region in France. According to Brigitte Roth, head of Française des jeux, the man is a “Loyal and regular player”.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>In a short interview with Française des jeux, the Frenchman speaks of being extremely happy to have won the  €162million. To the joy of the French public the man specifies that he wants to keep as much of the money in France as possible by investing in French real estate projects with which to stimulate the French economy. Such patriotism in light of such a huge cash windfall is surely striking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By finally claiming a slip of paper that cost him 2 euros, this man has entered into the top 250 richest people of France. His win of  €162,256,622 also makes him the second biggest Euromillions winner ever just behind Colin and Christine Weir who took home €185 million last July.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nPrevious articles: \r\n</p>\r\n<a href="/lottery-news/where-is-the-record-euromillions-winning-frenchman">Wheres the winning Euromillions frenchman</a>', 'French Euromillions Winner Collect Winnings', 'french euromillions winner, french winner, euromillions winner, euromillions', 'The to now unknown frenchman has come forward to collect his winnings according to the french national lottery', 2, 1319537544, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'French Euromillions Winner Collect Winnings', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1318514198, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (6, 6, 'en', 'scottish_couple_won_the_largest_ever_euromillions_jackpot', 'Scottish couple won the largest ever Euromillions jackpot', '<p>“When we first realised we had won, it felt like a dream. Everything went into slow motion."</em>    Chris Wier, 55, fully trained psychiatric nurse and husband Colin, 64, a former television cameraman have just become Europe’s biggest ever lottery winners after claiming the £161m <a href="http://euromillions.com">Euromillions</a> jackpot last Tuesday the 12th of July 2011.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple’s winning ticket matched all five main numbers, 17, 19, 38, 42 and 45 and both Lucky Stars 9 and 10.    Being capped after 11 successive rollovers the jackpot now places the couple from Falkirk at number 430 in this year’s Sunday Times Rich List and propels them past Angela Kelly the former highest Scottish <a href="http://euromillions.com/euromillions-winners/">Euromillions winners</a> who won the £35,425,411.80 Euromillions jackpot in August 2007. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nHaving checked the numbers three or four times the couple sat up all night in disbelief and utter shock waiting for the telephone line run by Camelot to open so they could claim their haul. “We were excited, exhilarated, we couldn''t sleep."    At the media conference in the Inchyra Grange hotel in Falkirk the Scottish couple spoke about what they are going to do with their winnings and how they will deal with this life  changing event.    The lucky winners have made immediate plans to travel and are excited about the once unattainable opportunities that have now become a reality. On their list is a visit to the Great Wall of China and Australia along with visiting famous art galleries. They also plan to  purchase new cars and homes for both themselves and for their son, Jamie, 22 who works in a local call centre and daughter Carly, 24 who is currently studying photography at university.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n“These are all things we thought we would never see." Chris Wier.    Before Tuesday''s draw, the largest Britsih Euromillions lottery winner was the player who bagged a staggering £113m last October and who chose to remain anonymous, closely followed by Nigel and Justine Page, from Gloucestershire, who won the jackpot prize of £56 m when they played the Euromillions lottery in February 2010.    Two other ticket holders from the UK lottery won £1.7m after they successfully matched five numbers and one Lucky Star on Tuesday’s unprecedented draw.</p>', 'Scottish couple won the largest ever Euromillions jackpot', 'Big Euromillions Win, Euromillions Winners, Scottish Couple, Euromillions Jackpot', 'A Scottish couple won the biggest Jackpot in the history of the Euromillions lottery.', 2, 1319483015, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'scottish couple', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1319483015, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (7, 7, 'en', 'missing_london_winner', 'Missing London Winner', '<p>Last Monday (31/10) it was revealed that a massive €109,703.40 of Euromillions prize money remains unclaimed! We can confirm that the ticket was purchased in London in the borough of Westminster.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naturally lottery bosses are urging everyone to double check their tickets to make sure the life changing sum meets with it''s rightful owner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winning ticket matched 5 of the main numbers of the Euromillions draw on the 27th September 2011. The winning numbers were 18, 27, 28, 35 and 40, with lucky stars 3 and 5.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winner has until 15:00 GMT on march 25th 2012 to claim their cash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the unfortunate eventuality of the money remaining unclaimed till then it will go to help those less fortunate. The prize money -plus interest- will go to the Good Causes, which has already raised over €30 billion for charity from lottery ticket sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A spokesperson for the National Lottery said: “We''re desperate to find this missing ticket-holder and unite them with their winnings – before their chance of claiming is blown sky high”, “We have the champagne on ice, our fingers crossed and fireworks on hand to help the ticket-holder celebrate should they come forward to claim their prize.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe you have the winning ticket for any  National Lottery draws you should call the official claimants line on 0845 910 0000.</p>', 'Missing London Winner', 'London winner, Euromillions winner, ', 'Last Monday (31/10) it was revealed that a massive €109,703.40 of Euromillions prize money remains unclaimed! We can confirm that the ticket was purchased in London in the borough of Westminster', 2, 1320271039, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Missing London Winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1320274639, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (8, 8, 'en', 'peugeot_workers_syndicate_win_millions', 'Peugeot Workers Syndicate Win Millions', '<p>The power of the lottery syndicates shows itself again today for a group of 13 Peugeot workers in Coventry. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The workers celebrate a €1,162,247 win, and take home a cool €89, 000 each from Friday''s <a href="/euromillions-uk-millionaire-raffle">Euromillions UK millionaire raffle</a>. The UK millionaire raffle has made the Euromillions very popular in the UK since entrants there get two chances to win with their entry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The syndicate has proven that 13 isn''t such an unlucky number as they take home their money. They all work together at the Torrington Avenue Peugeot site and have been entering the Euromillions twice-weekly for quite some time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The team of colleagues wish to remain anonymous but a spokesman for the syndicate was quoted to say</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\nWe are over the moon, and are looking forward to spending our winnings.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>We at Euromillions.com wish them all the best with their winnings and will be keeping our eyes peeled for the next smart syndicate to get lucky</p>', 'Syndicate Wins Millionaire Raffle', 'Euromillions, Syndicate, millionaire raffle', 'A lucky group of 13 Peugeot factory workers have scooped up the jackpot in the UK Millionaire Raffle', 2, 1320314822, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Peugeot Workers Syndicate Win Millions', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1320314822, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (9, 9, 'en', 'euromillions_winners_to_boost_political_party', 'Euromillions Winners To Boost Political Party', '<p>Euromillions winners Colin and Christine Weir may be set to boost the campaign of a local political party with a 7 figure sum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple who won the largest Euromillions jackpot of €187 million are supporters of the SNP (Scottish Nationalist Party). The news comes in light of a new independence referendum that the SNP will be raising funds for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Within 1 month of the couple scooping the huge prize they were hounded by begging letters and ran off to Spain. However one letter they received from Alex Salmond -leader of the SNP- was very welcome as he wrote to congratulate them on their win.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colin Weir who in his younger days volunteered his time to help produce party political broadcasts, has also run as a member of parliament for the party in his local area of Ayr.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yesterday an SNP source as reported to say that Mr Weir is “committed to giving a substantial seven-figure donation towards the referendum campaign -he wants to help the party make a difference."</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It remains to be seen exactly when this donation will be made and for how much, but the thought of Euromillions money changing the lay of the political land is an exciting one!</p>', 'Euromillions Winners To Boost SNP', 'Euromillions, winners, donations', 'A Scottish Nationalist political party may be set to receive a very large Euromillions windfall. Courtesy of Colin and Christine Weir winners of €186 million', 2, 1320663073, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Euromillions donation to SNP', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1320663073, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (10, 10, 'en', 'euromillions_jackpot_keeps_rolling', 'Euromillions Jackpot Keeps Rolling', '<p>This Friday night''s draw is becoming hotly anticipated as the Euromillions jackpot will be an estimated €66,000,000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once again Tuesday''s numbers did not produce a jackpot winner. For the fifth consecutive draw the Euromillions has rolled over and this new jackpot will start to encourage even more entrants into the lottery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It will be of interest to many to know that the last time there was a fifth rollover,  the jackpot continued to grow to €150 million. Will we all be buying our tickets for a huge jackpot of over €100 million? Or will your lucky numbers be coming up this Friday to bring you home a massive prize? Only time will tell, but one thing is for sure, the excitement grows with the prize fund!</p>', 'Euromillions Jackpot Keeps Rolling', 'Euromillions, rollover, jackpot', 'Ticket sales due to rise for Friday''s draw, as another Euromillions rollover creates a huge jackpot', 2, 1320920095, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Euromillions Jackpot Keeps Rolling', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1320920095, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (11, 11, 'en', 'euromillions_results_for_friday_11th_november', 'EuroMillions results for Friday 11th November', '<p>The massive rollover jackpot that had captivated the attention of many has been won by a lucky citizen of Switzerland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the moment the winner has yet to make himself public but it is known for sure that the Swiss national has won € 67,939,184. A massive sum that was desired by many.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike the winners from other countries in the Euromillions the Swiss player will have to pay tax on his winnings, meaning he will not receive his entire sum up front. This may add a bit more rationality to his Euromillions spending!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The numbers 1 and 4 were lucky this week appearing in both draws. Maybe in next weeks draws it will be time to pick some different numbers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This win marks the end of the big rollovers for now, and sets this Tuesday''s prize back to €15 million, still a handsome figure that we will all have our eyes on.</p>', 'EuroMillions results for Friday 11th November', 'Euromillions, Winner, Switzerland', 'After 5 consecutive rollovers the EuroMillions Jackpot of € 67,939,184 goes to a lucky ticket holder bought in Switzerland.', 2, 1321006255, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'EuroMillions results for Friday 11th November', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321006255, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (12, 7, 'de', 'londoner_gewinner_gesucht', 'Londoner gewinner gesucht', '<p>Heute stellt sich heraus, dass eine Gewinnsumme von €109,703.40 von Euromillions nicht ausgezahlt wurde. Wir können bestätigen, dass das Ticket im Londoner Stadtteil Westminster gekauft wurde.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selbstverständlich bitten die Chefs der Lotterie dringend darum, die Lose genau nachzuprüfen, um sicherzustellen, dass die lebensverändernde Summe dem rechtmäßigen Eigentümer zugestellt werden kann. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Gewinnerlos hatte die 5 Hauptnummern der Euromillions Ziehung vom 27. September 2011. Die richtigen Zahlen waren 18,27,28, 35 und 40, mit den Glückszahlen 3 und 5. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Gewinner hat bis zum 25. März 2012 bis 15:00 Uhr GTM Zeit, um sein Geld zu erhalten.\r\nFalls der unglückliche Fall auftreten sollte, dass das Geld bis dahin nicht angefordert wird, wird das Geld den weniger Glücklichen helfen. Die Gewinnsumme - plus Zinsen- wird für wohltätige Zwecke verwendet. Über €30 Billionen sind schon durch nicht ausgezahlte Gewinne gespendet worden. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ein Sprecher der National Lotterie sagte: „Wir suchen verzweifelt nach dem Losinhaber und wollen Ihm den Gewinn zu Gute kommen lassen- bevor der Anspruch auf den Gewinn verfällt“. Wir haben den Champagner Eis gekühlt, unsere Daumen gedrückt und Feuerwerk für den Losinhaber bereit um zu feiern, falls er sich zur Gewinnausschüttung melden sollte.  \r\nWenn Sie glauben, Sie haben das Gewinner-Los für alle National Lotterien gezogen, dann sollten Sie sich unter der Nummer +44 845 910 0000 melden. </p>', 'Londoner gewinner gesucht', 'Londoner gewinner gesucht', 'Heute stellt sich heraus, dass eine Gewinnsumme von €109,703.40 von Euromillions nicht ausgezahlt wurde. Wir können bestätigen, dass das Ticket im Londoner Stadtteil Westminster gekauft wurde.', 1, 1321960241, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Missing London Winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321021099, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (13, 10, 'es', 'el_bote_euromillones_se_sigue_renovando', 'El bote Euromillones se sigue renovando', '<p>El sorteo de este viernes se está haciendo esperar ya que el bote Euromillones se estima a €66 millones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Una vez más los números del último martes no llevaron a un ganador del bote. Por el quinto sorteo consecutivo el bote de la Euromillones se renovo y este nuevo bote lleva a los jugadores a animarse aun más a participar en la lotería.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les parecerá útil a muchos saber que la última vez que el bote se renovó cinco veces consecutivamente el bote siguió aumentando hasta 150 millones de euros. ¿Compraremos todos entradas para un bote de más de €100 millones? ¿O su selección de números coincidirá con la selección ganadora de este viernes? Sólo el tiempo lo dirá, ¡pero una cosa segura es que la excitación crece al mismo tiempo que el bote!</p>', 'El bote Euromillones se sigue renovando', 'euromillones, euromillions, bote, renovacion, ', 'El bote euromillones se sigue renovando y este viernes alcanza 66 millones de euros. Por la quinta semana consecutiva el bote euromillones se renueva y tal vez esta noche aumente todavía más.', 2, 1321980762, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Euromillions Jackpot Keeps Rolling', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321023938, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (14, 9, 'es', 'ganadores_quieren_invertir_en_un_partido_politico', 'Ganadores quieren invertir en un partido político', '<p>Colin y Christine Weir, ganadores del Euromillones en Julio podrían dar una mano a un partido político con una suma de siete números.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La pareja que ganó €187 millones -lo que representa el bote más alto jamás ganado en la lotería Euromillones- son partidarios de la SNP (Scottish Nationalist Party - Partido Nacionalista Escocés). La noticia conlleva un nuevo referéndum independiente para el que la SNP recaudará fondos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dentro del mes que recogieron el enorme premio la pareja fue perseguida por cartas de mendigares y huyó a España. Sin embargo, una carta que recibieron de parte de Alex Salmond, líder de la SNP, fue la muy bien bienvenida ya que les felicitó por la increíble ganancia. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colin Weir, que en su juventud ofreció su tiempo para ayudar a producir emisiones de los partidos políticos también se hizo miembro del parlamento por el partido de su área local ‘Ayr’.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ayer, una fuente de la SNP informó que el Señor Weir está “comprometido a dar una importante donación de siete cifras para el referéndum de la campaña -quiere ayudar el partido a hacer una diferencia.”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Falta por saber exactamente cuando esta donación se realizará y de cuánto será, pero la idea de invertir el dinero de Euromillones en el terreno político es muy interesante.</p>', 'Ganadores quieren invertir en un partido político', 'euromillones, ganadores, partido, político, bote,', 'Una pareja escocesa que ganó en julio de 2011 el bote más elevado de la lotería Euromillones, quiere ayudar económicamente un partido político en Escocia.', 2, 1322305255, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Euromillions donation to SNP', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321024783, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (15, 12, 'en', 'euromillions_prize_saves_last_ocean_paddle_steamer', 'Euromillions Prize Saves Last Ocean Paddle Steamer', '<p>The worlds last ocean going paddle steamer is set to be rescued by a donation from Euromillions winners Colin and Christine Weir.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Waverley steamer sails all over Britain but due to rising upkeep costs was due to retire. The town of Largs greatly depends on its tourism and the Waverley brings a lot of money into their local economy. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>A source close to the couple said: “The Weirs have very big hearts and they just love Largs and the community of Ayrshire”. Chris Weir himself was quoted: “We are in discussions with the Waverley people as we regard the ship as iconic. It has a place in our childhoods – and it is high on our list of causes that should be helped”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chairman of the Waverley''s development board said: “The generosity of Chris and Colin Weir has been wonderful”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It isn''t the first gesture of charity from the philanthropic couple, having already pledged a 7 figure sum to local political party the SNP. They have also bought houses for their close friends, and gave their old home to their neighbour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colin and Christine will continue to put their Euromillions prize money to good use, not only for their friends but the community and its economy on the whole.</p>', 'Euromillions Prize Saves Last Ocean Paddle Steamer', 'Euromillions Charity, Paddle Steamer, Euromillions winner', 'The winners of €161 million are set to continue boosting their local economy. Their charitable donations will save a popular tourist attraction', 2, 1321092839, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Euromillions Prize Saves Last Ocean Paddle Steamer', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321092839, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (16, 8, 'es', 'pena_peugeot_gana_1_200_000', 'Peña Peugeot gana €1 200 000', '<p>El poder de jugar en peña en una lotería se manifesta nuevamente hoy para un grupo de 13 trabajadores de Peugeot en Coventry. Los trabajadores celebran una victoria de €1 165 000 y llevan a casa €90 000 cada uno. El sorteo millonario del Reino Unido ha hecho que el Euromillones está muy popular en este país desde que participantes tienen dos oportunidades de ganar con su entrada. La peña ha demostrado que el 13 no tiene mucho de un número de mala suerte. Todos trabajan juntos en el lugar de Torrington Avenue Peugeot y estaban jugando dos veces por semana en la Euromillones desde hace bastante tiempo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> El grupo de colegas desean permanecer en el anonimato. Sin embargo, un portavoz de la peña dice:</br>\r\n"<i>Estamos en la luna y con muchas ganas de aprovechar de nuestras ganancias.</i>"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nosotros, en <a href="http://euromillions.com/es" title="Inicio Euromillions.com">Euromillions.com</a>, les deseamos todo lo mejor con su ganancia y esperamos que ganen otra vez!</p>', 'Peña Peugeot gana €1 200 000', 'Euromillones, peña, sindicato, sorteo millonario', 'Una Peña en el Reino Unido gana 1,2 millones de euros al Euromillones. Hacia tiempo que participaban en la loteria y finalmente ganaron un gran bote todos juntos. Están impacientes aprovechar del dinero que  ', 2, 1322575385, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Peugeot Workers Syndicate Win Millions', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321099995, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (17, 13, 'de', 'euromillionen_jackpot_gewinner_15_november', 'Euromillionen Jackpot Gewinner 15 November', '<p>Ein sehr seltenes Ereignis, ein weiterer Euromillionen Jackpot findet nur vier Tage nach dem letzten statt. Selbstverständlich kann der Gewinn nicht mit den € 67 Millionen Euro verglichen werden die letzten Freitag an einen glücklichen Schweizer Teilnehmer gingen. Mit gestern im Jackpot befindlichen € 15 Millionen Euro wird der Gewinner trotzdem glücklich sein.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Gewinner muss sich noch melden, aber die Lotterie Bosse können bestätigen, dass das Ticket definitive in Großbritannien gekauft wurde. Wir raten jedem in Großbritannien zu prüfen und nochmalig zu prüfen; klicken sie hier für die neusten <a href="{{lottery_url::latest}}">Euromillionen Ergebnisse</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weitere News dazu, wenn es Neuigkeiten gibt. Im Moment lässt es viele von uns fragen, Rollover oder ein gewöhnlicher Jackpot Gewinn?</p>', 'Euromillionen Jackpot Gewinner 15 November', 'Euromillionen, Gewinner, 15 November', 'Der Gewinner muss sich noch melden, aber die Lotterie Bosse können bestätigen, dass das Ticket definitive in Großbritannien gekauft wurde.', 1, 1321952893, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Euromillionen Jackpot Gewinner 15 November', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321350588, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (18, 14, 'en', 'euromillions_jackpot_winner_15th_november', 'Euromillions Jackpot Winner 15th November', '<p>In a rare occurrence another Euromillions jackpot has been one just 4 days after the last one. Naturally the prize won can''t compare to the €67 million won by Friday''s lucky Swiss entrant. With €15,000,000 as yesterday''s jackpot we believe the winner will be happy regardless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winner has yet to come forward, however lottery bosses can confirm that the ticket was definitely purchased in the UK. We advise everyone in the UK to check and double check their tickets, for the latest results click <a href="/euromillions-results">here</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>More news on this as it develops. For the moment it leaves many of us wondering what is best, big rollovers or regular jackpot wins?</p>', 'Euromillions Jackpot Winner 15th November', 'Tuesday 15th, euromillions winner, Jackpot', 'The Euromillions Jackpot from Tuesday 15th November has been quickly snapped up before a rollover could start', 2, 1321978325, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Tuesday 15th November Winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321351577, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (19, 15, 'en', 'millionaire_month', 'Millionaire Month', '<p>Lottery bosses look set to make this year a very merry Christmas for players in the UK; using the <a href="http://euromillions.com/euromillions-uk-millionaire-raffle" target="_blank"> Millionaire Raffle</a> to create <strong>fifty guaranteed millionaires</strong> in the space of a month. While there haven''t been any announcements for the other European countries at the moment we sincerely hope a similar offer is extended to the other countries participating in the Euromillions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More information on the <a=http://euromillions.com/euromillions-uk-millionaire-raffle >UK Millionaire Raffle</a> can be found behind the link, but essentially the Millionaire Raffle guarantees winners by assigning each person a completely unique code, one code is a guaranteed winner of £1,000,000 the others are not. What makes the millionaire month unique is that on the 25th of November not one but <b>eighteen</b> people will receive a code for a guaranteed £1 million. Then each of the 7 Euromillions draws in the run up to Christmas will guarantee another millionaire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <strong>greatest Christmas present</strong> yet comes on the 23rd of December just before Christmas day. Guaranteed millionaire codes won''t be given to just a few, or even eighteen, but <strong>TWENTY-FIVE</strong>. So as the citizens of the UK hang up their stockings and eagerly await Christmas day, another twenty five of them will become millionaires!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fifty millionaires in one month guaranteed! It''s a tall order for the lottery providers but they will deliver and many people will be enjoying what will no doubt be their most memorable Christmas yet! A similar celebratory event was held in winter 2010 however at that time only twenty-five people were made millionaires. Now the ante is being upped and twice as many people will experience that joy as the previous year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will be updating the site with the winning raffle codes as they happen, so be sure to come and check the raffle results at www.euromillions.com</p>', 'Millionaire Month', 'Millionaire Month, Euromillions, Guaranteed Million', 'Many players in the UK look set to become guaranteed millionaires with the festive season Millionaire Month', 2, 1321524611, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Millionaire Month', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321524611, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (20, 16, 'de', 'euromillionsgewinn_rettet_den_letzten_ozean_raddampfer', 'Euromillionsgewinn rettet den letzten Ozean Raddampfer.', '<p>Der weltgrößte Ozean Raddampfer wird, dank einer Spende von den Euromillions Gewinnern Colin und Christine Weir, gerettet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Waverley genannte Dampfer fährt ganz Großbritannien entlang, aber aufgrund der immer höheren Unterhaltskosten sollte er in den Ruhestand gehen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Stadt Largs hängt stark vom Tourismus ab und der Raddampfer Waverley ist eine wichtige Einkommensquelle für die lokale Wirtschaft.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eine nahe Quelle des Paares sagt: ”Die Weirs haben ein sehr großes Herz und sie lieben einfach Largs und die Gemeinde Ayrshire.”Chris Weir selbst soll gesagt haben: ”Wir führen Gespräche mit den Waverley Vertretern, da wir das Schiff als eine Ikone ansehen. Es hat einen Platz in unseren Kindheitserinnerungen – und steht ganz oben auf unserer Liste, für Zwecke bei denen wir helfen sollen”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Vorsitzende von Waverley`s sagte: ” Die Großzügigkeit von Chris und Colin Weir war einfach großartig”\r\nEs ist nicht die erste Geste des wohltätigen Paares, nachdem sie bereits einen siebenstelligen Betrag an die lokale Politikpartei SNP gespendet hatten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sie haben auch Häuser für ihre engen Freunde gekauft und ihr altes Haus einem Nachbarn gegeben. \r\nColin und Christine werden auch weiterhin ihren Euromillions Gewinn für gute Zwecke verwenden, nicht nur für ihre Freunde, sondern für die Gemeinde und die lokale Wirtschaft.</p>', 'Euromillionsgewinn rettet den letzten Ozean Raddampfer', 'Ozean Raddampfer, Euromillionen, Gewinn', 'Der weltgrößte Ozean Raddampfer wird, dank einer Spende von den Euromillions Gewinnern Colin und Christine Weir, gerettet.', 1, 1321868668, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Euromillionsgewinn Ozean Raddampfer', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1321868668, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (21, 17, 'en', 'uk_millionaire_raffle_month_draw_nov_25th', 'UK Millionaire Raffle Month Draw, Nov 25th ', '<p>This month there was 18 new millionaires in the United Kingdom. The first 18 of a total of 50 winners that are each going to receive £1,000,000 was revealed on the Friday 25th of November, see the raffle codes below. To participate in this event hosted by the UK National Lottery you must be sure to buy your ticket from an UK ticket outlet to receive your raffle code.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the 23rd of December another 25 lucky UK residents will become guaranteed millionaires, and each Euromillions draw till then will have the usual Millionaire raffle. Click for more <a href=http://euromillions.com/millionaire-month>Millionaires Month</a> information.\r\n\r\n<p>The UK National Lottery''s Millionaire Month Raffle Results Nov. 25</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>QTK867932</li>\r\n<li>RTP724614</li>\r\n<li>VVH599778</li>\r\n<li>VVJ341321</li>\r\n<li>VVL035544</li>\r\n<li>VVL072570</li>\r\n<li>VVM036610</li>	\r\n<li>VVM977572</li>\r\n<li>VVP017360</li>	\r\n<li>VVQ059518</li>	\r\n<li>VVQ376718</li>	\r\n<li>VVQ387776</li>\r\n<li>VVR165019</li>	\r\n<li>VVR198356</li>	\r\n<li>VVR288026</li>	\r\n<li>VVS586769</li>\r\n<li>VVT048882</li>	\r\n<li>VVT537436</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', 'UK Millionaire Raffle Month Draw, Nov 25th ', 'UK Millionaire Raffle, Euromillions, Draw, 18 Winners', 'In this first months Millionaire Month Draw hosted by the UK National Lottery there''s a total of 18 raffle winners. Check the raffle results here', 2, 1322491104, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'UK Millionaire Raffle Month Draw Nov 25th ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322301725, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (22, 18, 'es', 'ganancia_del_bote_de_35_000_000', 'Ganancia del bote de €35 000 000', '<p> El sorteo del viernes 25 de noviembre se realizaba después de dos renovaciones consecutivas del bote, alcanzando 35 millones de euros, y podía ocurrir una tercera renovación en el caso de que nadie hubiera ganado. Sin embargo, en cada sorteo existe la posibilidad de ganar 13 premios diferentes. Aquí se encuentra toda la información acerca de <a href="http://euromillions.com/es/estructura-premios-loteria-euromillones" title="Euromillones - Estructura de los premios">las categorías de premios</a> que se pueden ganar en la lotería Euromillones.\r\n\r\n<p> El bote de este viernes 25 de noviembre de 2011 ponía en juego la suma de 35 millones de euros. Una entrada comprada en el Portugal coincidió con la selección ganadora del sorteo y se lleva el bote! La <strong>combinación ganadora</strong> del sorteo del 25 de noviembre es: <strong>14 - 19 - 26 - 28 - 34</strong> Estrellas: <strong>5 - 8</strong>. El acertante de primera categoría no se hizo conocer todavía pero 3,5 millones de premios de otras categorías fueron ganados. De estos premios, se ganaron 11 premios de segunda categoría, que se gana por hacer coincidir 5 números principales más un número estrella. Para este sorteo; el premio de segunda categoría alcanzaba €180 000. En total, en el sorteo de este viernes 25 de noviembre, la lotería Euromillones repartió €59 276 257.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> El próximo sorteo se llevará a cabo el martes 29 de noviembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego -además de las 12 otras categorías de premio- el bote con su suma inicial de 15 millones de euros. ¡Ya se pueden <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/es/" title="Comprar entradas a la lotería Euromillones en Euromillions.com">comprar entradas</a> para el próximo sorteo!</p>', 'Ganancia del bote de €35 000 000', 'euromillones, euromillions, bote, ganado, ', 'En el sorteo Euromillones del viernes 25 de noviembre se podía ganar €35 000 000. En Portugal una entrada coincidió con la combinación ganadora del sorteo.', 2, 1322305099, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'jackpot-25-november', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322303924, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (23, 19, 'en', 'biggest_euromillions_winners_make_public_appearance', 'Biggest Euromillions Winners Make Public Appearance', '<p>The married couple from Scotland, Colin and Christine Weir, made their first public appearance on Friday night since winning their millions. They were to be the guests of honour at a fundraising dinner being held by the Scottish Nationalist Party (SNP), being held at the Thistle Hotel in Glasgow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The couple would have had a warm welcome as their recent donation of €1,000,000 is the largest the SNP have ever received, and it will surely be of great use to them in an upcoming referendum. The Weirs told SNP leader Alex Salmond that half the cash should be used to campaign for a “Yes” vote for in the next referendum for Scottish independence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They insisted though that their donation was about more than just “party politics”. Colin, 64 said: “Every society, every country should have the right to determine its own path. That''s something I''ve believed in strongly for a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The generous Weirs have since their big win bought their friends new cars, given their old house to a neighbours daughter, and even saved the historic Waverley paddle steamer from going out of business.</p>', 'Biggest Euromillions Winners Make Public Appearance', 'Euromillions Winners, Colin and Christine, SNP', 'The winners of the biggest Euromillions jackpot of €185 million have been wined and dined by a local political party after a big donation', 2, 1322486594, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Euromillions Winners Public', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322485741, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (24, 20, 'en', 'portuguese_winner_of_35million_on_fridays_jackpot', 'Portuguese Winner Of  €35Million on Friday''s jackpot', '<p>Friday''s Euromillion jackpot of a huge €35, 062, 896 has been won by 1 lucky ticket holder in Portugal. The winner won''t be sharing that amount with anyone and will no doubt remember the 25th of November 2011 as the start of a new life. The winning numbers were 14, 19, 26, 28 and 32, with Lucky Stars 05 and 08.\r\n\r\n<p>These numbers were lucky for more than 3.5 million winners, and the Euromillions cash is being shared all over. 11 tickets which matched 5 main numbers and one lucky star  have brought their owners €179, 533 Euros. 9 others have won €73, 143 by matching 4 out of 5 main numbers plus both lucky stars.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More winners were abound though as a further 118 people leave Fridays'' draw with an extra €2, 789 in their pockets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The UK got even more Euromillions love on Friday with 18 new millionaires created by the <a href=http://euromillions.com/uk-millionaire-raffle-month-draw-november-25th>UK Millionaire Month</a>.</p>', 'Portuguese Winner Of  €35Million on Friday''s jackpot', 'Portugal, Fridays Euromillions Winner', 'Friday''s Euromillions Jackpot goes to Portugal as many more people win lower tiered prizes', 2, 1322490499, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Portuguese Jackpot Winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322490382, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (25, 21, 'es', 'proximo_sorteo_29_de_noviembre_de_2011', 'Próximo Sorteo: 29 de Noviembre de 2011', '<p> El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar este martes 29 de noviembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego la suma inicial del bote, que equivale a 15 millones de euros. El sorteo del viernes pasado proponía 35 millones de euros y un boleto sellado en Portugal coincidió con la selección ganadora del sorteo, lo que lleva el bote de este martes a empezar de vuelta.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Los que descubren la lotería Euromillones y los recién llegados en <a href="http://euromillions.com/es" title="Inicio Euromillions.com/es">Euromillions.com</a> serán interesados en saber que proponemos Bonos. Se puede jugar la primera entrada libre de riesgo y se puede aconsejar el sitio a un amigo. La entrada libre de riesgo propone una entrada reembolsada en el caso de que no gane un premio. La opción de aconsejar el sitio a conocidos permite recibir una entrada gratis por persona aconsejada, y ¡la persona aconsejada también recibe una entrada gratis! Con este método simple y atractivo se puede crear una red de entradas gratis!</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Para aprender más acerca de los Bonos disponibles en Euromillions.com; visite la página <a href="http://play.euromillions.com/es/bonuses-and-rewards/" title="Aprender más acerca de los bonos Euromillones">Bonos Euromillones</a>.</p>', 'Próximo Sorteo: 29 de Noviembre', 'euromillones, euromillions, próximo, sorteo, ', 'El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar este martes 29 de noviembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego la suma inicial del bote, que equivale a 15 millones de euros.', 2, 1322492579, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Next-draw-29-november-2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322492038, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (26, 22, 'de', 'viele_gewinner_aber_noch_eine_verlaengerung', 'Viele Gewinner, aber noch eine Verlängerung', '<p>Der Dezember 2011 wird mit einer großen Gewinnsumme starten, da der Jackpot von\r\nNovember nicht geknackt worden ist. Am Freitag, den 2. Dezember wird durch eine\r\nEuromillions Verlängerung schätzungsweise €25, 000, 000 zu haben sein, und wir hoffen\r\nnatürlich, dass jemand mehr Glück haben wird, als bei der letzten Ziehung, den Jackpot zu\r\nknacken. Die Zahlen, die niemand richtig getippt hat, waren die 11, 25, 41, 45 und 50, mit den\r\nGlückszahlen 02 und 07.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wie sie wissen, hört der Spaß nicht auf, egal ob man der Gewinner ist oder nicht- es gibt\r\nfast immer einige große Gewinner in jeder Euromillions-Ziehung! In Großbritannien hat die\r\nMillionen Lotto-Nummer WVW309553 einen Gewinner mit einer stolzen Summe von £1\r\nMillionen glücklich gemacht!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ein Losinhaber hat den Jackpot um eine Zahl verpasst. Nachdem man 5 Zahlen und eine\r\nGlückszahl richtig getippt hat,ärgert man sich, doch die Lotto Organisatoren machten deutlich,\r\ndass der Gewinner eine Gewinnsumme von £720, 278 beanspruchen kann.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weitere 4 Gewinner werden ein breites Grinsen auf ihren Gesichtern tragen, denn durch ihre\r\nAbstimmung von nur 5 richtigen Zahlen wird jeder einzelne eine stattliche Summe von £60,\r\n023 erhalten. Es gibt lebensverändernde Gewinnsummen, egal ob der Jackpot geknackt ist oder\r\nnicht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Es gibt keinen Zweifel daran, die Euromillions-Lotterie zu spielen, wie man an den 1.58\r\nMillionen Gewinnern vom letztem Abend sehen kann!</p>', 'Viele Gewinner, aber noch eine Verlängerung', 'Viele Gewinner, Verlängerung, Nachtricht, Euromillionen 29 Nov', 'Der Dezember 2011 wird mit einer großen Gewinnsumme starten, da der Jackpot von November nicht geknackt worden ist. Am Freitag, den 2.', 1, 1322553303, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', '29-november-2011-draw', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322553303, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (27, 23, 'en', 'unclaimed_millions_in_the_uk', 'Unclaimed Millions In The UK', '<p>The UK Millionaire Raffle has made 18 new millionaires as of last Friday. The fun is due to continue as another 25 millionaires are guaranteed on the 23rd of December. With it''s raffle style rules and a clean £1,000,000 up for grabs it''s no wonder so many tickets have been sold.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Christmas Super Raffle has brought a whole new popularity to the game. News has developed concerning the previous super raffle in June of this year. News that there are still two winners from the draw dated <strong>June 7th 2011</strong> who have not claimed their £1 million.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do you live in the the areas of Cannock Chase, Staffordshire? Or the Metropolitan Borough of Stockport?</strong> If so you may still be holding onto a millionaire raffle ticket worth £1 million. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winning raffle numbers from the date in question were:</p>\r\n<p><ul>\r\n<li>MVY348186</li>\r\n<li>MVZ001857</li>\r\n<li>MWB201666 </li>\r\n<li>MWB264579</li>\r\n<li>MWB757695</li>\r\n<li>MWC424302</li>\r\n<li>MWD030338 </li>\r\n<li>MWD374105</li>\r\n<li>MWD419069</li>\r\n<li> MWG042994 </li>\r\n<li>MWG128846 </li>\r\n<li>MWG504212</li>\r\n<li>MWH028574</li>\r\n<li>MWH097149</li>\r\n<li>MWH560389</li>\r\n</ul></p>\r\n<p>If you believe you are holding the winning raffle ticket then you must make your claim as soon as possible as the deadline for claims on this lottery is <strong>Sunday the 3rd of December!</strong></p>', 'Unclaimed Millions In The UK', 'Millionaire Raffle, Unclaimed, Winners', 'An urgent message to anyone who bought a millionaire raffle ticket in June 2011.', 2, 1322571263, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Unclaimed Millionaire Raffle Tickets', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322571263, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (28, 22, 'en', 'plenty_of_winners_but_another_rollover', 'Plenty of winners but another rollover', '<p>December 2011 will start with a big cash prize offering as November''s final jackpot wasn''t snapped up. On Friday 2nd of December a Euromillions rollover of an estimated €25,000,000 will be up for grabs, and we certainly hope somebody will be luckier than last draw in winning it. The numbers that nobody could quite match all of were 11, 25, 41, 45 and 50, with Lucky Star numbers 02 and 07. With nearly all of the main numbers being on the high end of the scale it''s no wonder that this statistic beating Euromillions result didn''t create a jackpot winner this time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you will know the fun doesn''t end with who did or didn''t win the jackpot; there are nearly always some big winners in every Euromillions draw! In the UK the <strong>Millionaire Raffle number WVW309553</strong> made one lucky winner of a clean £1 million!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One ticket holder missed the jackpot by just 1 number. Having matched 5 numbers and 1 lucky star they may have been cursing, that would change no doubt when the lottery organisers revealed the winner would be claiming a prize of €1,000,862!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another 4 people will be wearing big grins today as their matching of just 5 main numbers will see them receiving a handsome sum of €83,405 each. Life changing amounts of money whether there''s a jackpot win involved or not.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Euromillions lottery pays out, and with 1.58 million winners of a cash prize last night there''s no doubting it.</p>', 'Euromillions Winners From Tuesday 29th November', 'Euromillions Rollover, no winner, ', 'Unusually high results see a jackpot rollover, but plenty of other winners...', 2, 1323157959, 11, 'Rory Renehan', '29-november-2011-draw', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322648546, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (29, 22, 'es', 'sorteo_martes_29_de_noviembre', 'Sorteo martes 29 de noviembre', '<p> El sorteo del martes 29 de noviembre ponía en juego el bote inicial de 15 millones de euros. Nadie coincidió con la selección ganadora del sorteo así que ocurre una renovación del bote. El próximo sorteo tendrá lugar el viernes dos de diciembre y pondrá en juego un bote estimado en €26 000 000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Las renovaciones de botes son la clave de la lotería Euromillones. Cada semana, el bote aumenta hasta que alguien lo gane. Gracias a este método de juego atractivo ¡Euromillones ya repartió premios como 185 millones de euros!</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Se encuentra una correlación interesante entre la suma del bote y el número de entradas en el sorteo en cuestión. Cuanto más alto es el bote, más jugadores participan en el sorteo. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Más información acerca de la <a href="http://euromillions.com/es/renovacion-del-bote-euromillones" title="Información acerca de la renovación del bote Euromillones">renovación del bote</a> Euromillones.</p>', 'Sorteo martes 29 de noviembre', 'euromillones, euromillions, sorteo, ', 'El sorteo del 29 de noviembre ponía en juego el bote inicial de €15 000 000. Nadie coincidió con la selección ganadora así que habrá una renovación del bote.', 2, 1322667637, 10, 'Michael Hermes', '29-november-2011-draw', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322667496, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (30, 24, 'en', 'christmas_giveaway', 'Christmas Giveaway', '<p><strong>Euromillions.com Christmas Giveaways!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Christmas we are giving away a host of prizes and cash to not one, or two, but <strong>one hundred</strong> lucky Euromillions.com visitors. This is a special Christmas give away in the true sense of the words, as there is <strong>no fee</strong> to enter. That''s right, it''s absolutely <strong>free</strong> to join in and be in with the chance of winning a great prize. Why not get into the festive spirit a bit early and try your luck at being one of the lucky <strong>one hundred</strong> winners?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a brand new <strong>Sony Playstation 3</strong> to give away, and a host of entire Lotería De Navidad (El Gordo) lottery tickets (billetes). If you''re unfamiliar with the El Gordo lottery it''s worth knowing that the cost of an entire ticket is €200 and the prize fund is over <strong>€2 BILLION</strong> this year. Find more details on <a href target="http://euromillions.com/elgordo-christmas-prizes" target="_blank">El Gordo prizes here</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>90 other players will also receive a €10 bonus for use on Euromillions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How Do I Win?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Winning is easy, fun and entry is free! Visit <a href="http://www.euromillions.com/xmas" target="_blank">Euromillions.com/xmas</a> and register to play our free online Christmas lottery game. Simply pick and match your numbers in our instant lottery draw game. You may play in up to 5 draws per day and it''s always free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you match numbers you score points that are saved to your account. Players will be ranked by how many points they have at the end of the game, everybody in the top 100 will win a prize, but naturally the better you rank the better the prize.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Play every day as many as 5 times to accumulate as many points as you can! On the 20th the game will end and the winners will be announced. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>1st Place Prize – Sony Playstation 3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2nd to 10th Place Prize – An Entire <a href="http://euromillions.com/ElGordo-Christmas-Prizes" target="_blank">El Gordo Christmas Lottery ticket</a> -worth €200.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11th to 100th Place Prize - €10 Euromillions.com bonus</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Play To Win</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remember you''ve got to be in it to win it, the more you play the more points you win, the more points you win the better you rank, the better you rank the more chance you have of winning one of the top prizes!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Winners will be announced and notified by email on the 20th December.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Start earning your points here now and Merry Christmas one and all!</p>', 'Christmas Giveaway', 'Christmas, Free Lottery', 'Want to win some prizes for free? We''ve got lots of gifts to giveaway this year so join in for free to win!', 2, 1322826155, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Christmas 2011 giveaway', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322740056, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (31, 24, 'es', 'ofertas_de_navidad_de_euromillions_com', 'Ofertas de navidad de Euromillions.com', '<h3>Ofertas de navidad de Euromillions.com</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Durante esta navidad ofrecemos una cantidad importante de premios y dinero a cien afortunados visitantes de Euromillions.com. Es literalmente una oferta especial para navidad ya que no hay precio de entrada. Exactamente, participar en el juego es enteramente gratis y tendrá la posibilidad de ganar verdaderos premios interesantes. ¿Para que no entrara temprano en la competición festiva intentando su suerte para ser uno de los cien afortunados ganadores?\r\nSe puede ganar una nueva Sony Playstation 3 y una multitud de Boletos para la lotería de navidad El Gordo. Si usted no está muy familiarizado con la lotería de navidad El Gordo vale la pena saber que el costo de un boleto entero es de €200 y que este año el fondo de premios es de más de €2 mil millones. Encuentre <a href="http://euromillions.com/es/informacion-el-gordo-de-navidad" title="Obtener más información acerca de los premios El Gordo">más información acerca de los premios El Gordo</a>.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Además de estos premios, 90 otros jugadores recibirán un bono de 10€ utilizables en Euromillions.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>¿Cómo puedo ganar?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>¡Ganar es fácil, divertido y la entrada al juego es enteramente gratuita! Visite www.euromillions.com/xmas y regístrese para jugar en línea a nuestro juego gratis de Navidad. El juego es simple; consiste simplemente en elegir y acertar los números como en cualquier otra lotería. Se puede jugar un máximo de 5 entradas por día y siempre es gratis. Cuando acierte números de su selección con la selección ganadora del juego se ganan puntos que se guardan en su cuenta. Los jugadores serán clasificados según la cantidad de puntos que tienen. Los cien primeros ganaran un premio, y naturalmente, los más puntos mejor es el premio.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>¡Juegue todos los días sus 5 entradas para acumular lo más puntos posibles! El 20 de diciembre se termina el juego y se harán conocer los ganadores.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>Premios</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Premio único para el ganador: Sony Playstation 3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Premio para el segundo ganador hasta el décimo ganador: Un boleto para la Lotería de Navidad el Gordo. Valor: 200€.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Premios para el Undécimo ganador al centésimo ganador: Un bono de 10€ en Euromillions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Jugar para ganar</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Recuerde que hay que tomar enteramente parte al juego para ganar. Cuanto más juegue más puntos se ganan, más puntos ganados mejor será su rango, ¡y mejor es su rango más posibilidades tendrá de ganar uno de los los principales premios!</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Los ganadores serán anunciados y notificados por correo electrónico el 20 de diciembre.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Empiece ahora a colectar puntos y deseamos una Feliz Navidad a todos.</p>', 'Ofertas de navidad de Euromillions.com', 'euromillones, eurmillions, navidad,', 'En Euromillions.com ofrecemos premios enteramente gratis para la Navidad 2011. Aprenda más acerca de las ofertas.', 2, 1322826959, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Christmas 2011 giveaway', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322741257, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (32, 25, 'de', 'syndikat_macht_grossen_gewinn_beim_ersten_ticket', 'Syndikat macht großen Gewinn beim ersten Ticket', '<p>Glück kommt in vielen Formen für viele Menschen, aber für 25 Mitarbeiter und Stamm des Beech Tree pub in Cheshire, Großbritannien haben zum ersten mal dieses Glück. Ihr Verband- bestehend aus Stammkunden und Mitarbeitern in dem Pub- hat mit ihre allerersten Euromillions Ticket £1,000,000 (€1.16 million) gewonnen! Der Gewinn wu der britischen Millionär Verlosung geschöpft, der letzte Woche 18 Millionäre garantie Verbandsmitglieder haben bereits €46,000 mit ihrem allerersten Versuch bei Euromillionen gewonnen, und man sieht wirklich die Stärke des Spielens in einer Gruppe. Postarbeit Verbandsleiter David Edwards (52) konnte erst gar nicht glauben, dass sie gewonnen und sagte, dass sie sich alle im Pub unterhielten und beschlossen haben, dass sie alle garantierten £ 1 Millonen Preisen einen Verband gründen würden- ,,ich habe niemals dass wir einer der Gewinner sein werden.“</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>„Ich habe dies zweimal überprüft, weil ich unser Glück nicht fassen konnte.“</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nachdem Herr Edwards 18 Monate lang nicht in der Lage war aus finanziellen Gründe Auto zu reparieren,wird er dies mit seinem Gewinn als erstes tun. Herr Edwards ist ni einzige Verbandsmitglied mit Plänen für das Geld. Gastwirt Steve Hough (59) hat nich Reise nach Australien im Januar gebucht, sondern verspricht außerdem dieses Jahr ei besonderes Weihnachtsfest in seinem Pub zu feiern. Samantha Dickinson (26) wird eine Anzahlung auf die erste eigene Immobilie leisten. Gemeinsam mit ihrem Mann und ihrem Kind, sind sie jetzt in der Lage auf dem Immobilienmarkt mitzuhalten, auch in den wirtschaftlich schwierigen Zeiten. „Ich bin hocherfreut“, sagt sie. ,,Es gab vorher keine Möglichkeit in den Immobilienmarkt einz Allein die Kaution zu zahlen, ist in dieser Zeit so gut wie gar nicht mehr möglich.“ </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Verbleibende Mitglieder werden natürlich ein großzügiges Weihnachtsfest feiern. Die werden im Ausland gebucht und neue Autos gekauft.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Verbandsleiter David Edwards sagte, dass der „Mighty Reds“ Verband auch weiterhin wird und wir wünschen ihnen viel Glück für ihrer Zukunft. Um Herrn Edwards zu zitier diesem Ereignis wird uns niemand stoppen.“</p>', 'Syndikat macht großen Gewinn beim ersten Ticket', 'Euromillionen, Gewinn, Ersten, UK', 'Ihr Verband- bestehend aus Stammkunden und Mitarbeitern in dem Pub- hat mit ihre allerersten Euromillions Ticket £1,000,000 (€1.16 million) gewonnen!', 1, 1323158677, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Pub syndicate wins big on first raffle', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322811852, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (33, 25, 'en', 'syndicate_wins_big_on_first_ever_ticker', 'Syndicate Wins Big On First Ever Ticker', '<p>Luck comes in many forms for many people but for 25 staff and regulars at the Beech Tree pub in Cheshire UK, the first time is a charm. Their syndicate -made up of regular customers and staff at the pub- won £1,000,000 (€1.16 million) on their <strong>very first</strong> Euromillions ticket! The win was scooped on the UK Millionaire Raffle which guaranteed 18 millionaires last week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Syndicate members have each profited €46,000 from their first attempt at a Euromillions syndicate, and it really goes to show the power of playing in a group. Post office worker and syndicate leader David Edwards (52) couldn''t believe at first that they had won, and said that “We were all chatting in the pub and decided as there would be 18 guaranteed £1 million prizes, we would form a syndicate -I never thought we would be one of the winners”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“I had to double check in two different places because I could not believe our luck”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After 18 months of being unable to afford to get his car back on the road, Mr Edwards has plans for his big win already. Mr Edwards isn''t the only syndicate member with plans for the money, pub landlord Steve Hough (59), has already booked a holiday to Australia in January and is promising an extra special Christmas at the pub this year!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>26 year old syndicate member Samantha Dickinson will be putting the deposit down on her very first home, able now to get onto  the property market in difficult economic times with her new husband and child. “I''m delighted” she said “There was no chance of getting on the property ladder before now. Just to get the deposit these days is impossible”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remaining syndicate members will of course this year be having the most lavish Christmases they''ve ever had. Holidays are being booked abroad and new cars are being bought.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Syndicate leader David Edwards said the ''Mighty Reds'' syndicate will continue to play, and we say more power to them and best of luck with their future entries. To quote Mr Edwards “After this, there will be no stopping us”</p>', 'Syndicate Wins Big On First Ever Ticket', 'Syndicate, Millionaire Raffle, Euromillions', 'Beginners luck strikes a local pub in the UK and makes 25 syndicate members wealthy for Christmas', 2, 1322826952, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Pub syndicate wins big on first raffle', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1322826952, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (34, 26, 'en', 'euromillions_jackpot_won_in_france', 'Euromillions Jackpot Won In France', '<p>For the draw on Friday 2nd of December one lucky winning ticket is eligible to grab the €27,094,319 jackpot. The winner has yet to come forward to claim their ticket but we wager that it won''t be long before the player makes themselves known to the La Francaise des Jeux (FDJ) to lay their hands on their well earned win.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The winning numbers 27, 40, 7, 43, 30 with lucky stars 8 and 9 were sold on a ticket  in the tobacco department of a shop in Côte-d''Or. For security reasons the FDJ are reluctant to reveal the exact location of the shop in question.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At this stage it is still impossible to know if the winner is a Côte d''Orient or if they are of foreign origin and were simply visiting the area when they bought a ticket. In any event the FDJ is urging everybody who may be of the area or bought a ticket there to double check to see if they have won.</p>', 'Jackpot Winner For Friday 2nd December Confirmed', 'Euromillions Jackpot, Friday''s Jackpot Winner', 'The Euromillions jackpot of almost €28 million has been won with a ticket in France', 2, 1323102186, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Jackpot Won In France December 2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323095654, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (35, 26, 'es', 'ganancia_del_bote_de_27_000_000', 'Ganancia del bote de €27 000 000', '<p>Para el sorteo del viernes 02 de diciembre hubo un afortunado ganador del bote de €27 094 319. El ganador aún no se ha presentado para reclamar su premio, pero estimamos que no durará mucho tiempo antes de que el jugador se haga conocer de la Française des Jeux (FDJ) para colectar su premio.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La selección ganadora 07, 27, 30, 40, 43 con las estrellas 8 y 9 se vendió en un boleto en un estanco del departamento Côte-d''Or, en Francia. Por razones de seguridad la FDJ es reacia a revelar la ubicación exacta del estanco en cuestión.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hasta ahora no se puede saber si el ganador viene de Côte d''Orient o si es de origen extranjero y que era simplemente de paseo en la zona cuando el boleto se compro. En cualquier caso, la FDJ pide a todos los que sean de la zona o los que hayan comprado un boleto cerca verificar dos veces si han ganado.</p>', 'Ganancia del bote de €27 000 000', 'euromillones, euromillions, bote, ganado,', 'El sorteo del 02 de diciembre de 2011 ponía en juego la suma de 27 millones de euros y hubo un afortunado ganador que compro el boleto en Francia.', 2, 1323098223, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Jackpot Won In France December 2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323098133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (36, 24, 'de', 'weinachtsgeschenk', 'Weinachtsgeschenk', '<p>Diese Weihnachten verlosen wir eine Vielzahl von Preisen, um nicht nur einen oder zwei,\r\nsondern hundert Euromillions.com Besucher glücklich zu machen. Dies ist ein besonderes\r\nWeihnachtsgeschenk im wahrsten Sinne des Wortes, da keine Gebühren anfallen. Das ist\r\nrichtig- es ist aboslut kostenlos mitzumachen und die Chance zu haben, einen tollen Preis zu\r\ngewinnen. Warum nicht ein bisschen früher in die festliche Stimmung kommen und versuchen\r\neiner der hundert glücklichen Gewinner zu werden?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wir haben eine brandneue Playstation 3 zu verschenken, und außerdem eine Menge von\r\nLotería de Navidad (El Gordo) Lottoscheinen (billetes). Falls sie nicht mit der El Gordo Lotterie\r\nvertraut sind, ist es wichtig zu wissen, dass der Wert für ein Ticket €200 beträgt. Der Gewinn\r\nbeträgt jedoch dieses Jahr €2 BILLIONEN. Weitere Details für El Gordo Preise finden sie hier</p>\r\n\r\n<p>90 weitere Spieler erhalten außerdem einen €10 Bonus für den Einsatz auf Euromillions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wie gewinne ich?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gewinnen ist einfach, macht Spaß und der Eintritt ist frei! Besuchen sie Euromillions.com/\r\nxmas und registrieren sie sich, um bei unserer kostenlosen Weihnachtslotterie mitzuspielen.\r\nEinfach Zahlen in unserem vorliegenden Lotterieziehungsspiel aussuchen. Sie können an bis zu\r\n5 Ziehungen pro Tag teilnehmen, kostenlos!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wenn ihre Zahlen übereinstimmen, bekommen sie Punkte, die ihrem Account zugeschrieben\r\nwerden. Die Spieler werden durch ihre Punkte am Ende des Spiels eingestuft. Jeder, der dann\r\nin der TOP 100 ist, gewinnt einen Preis, aber je besser der Rang des Spielers ist, desto besser ist\r\nder Preis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spielen Sie jeden Tag 5 mal um so viele Punkte wie möglich zu sammeln! Am 20. ist das Spiel zu\r\nEnde und die Gewinner werden bekannt gegeben.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li><p>1. Platz: Sony Playstation 3</p></li>\r\n\r\n<li><p>2. bis 10. Platz: Ein El Gordo Weihnachts Lotterie Ticket- im Wert von €200</p></li>\r\n\r\n<li><p>11. bis 100. Platz: €10 Euromillions.com Bonus</p></li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'Weinachtsgeschenk', 'Weinachtsgeschenk, Freispielen', 'Diese Weihnachten verlosen wir eine Vielzahl von Preisen, um nicht nur einen oder zwei, sondern hundert Euromillions.com Besucher glücklich zu machen.', 1, 1323156874, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Christmas 2011 giveaway', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323156874, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (37, 27, 'en', 'secret_millionaire_the_generosity_of_winners', 'Secret Millionaire & The Generosity Of Winners', '<p>With a French winner taking last week''s rollover jackpot of €27 million, this night will have us eagerly awaiting the results to see if this streak of regular winners will continue, or if the €15 million will rollover into a truly enormous amount. Today take a look at the UK''s quietest new millionaire, and some previous winners who have this year brought an early Christmas to those less fortunate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a week now Paul Turton has been withholding from his friends, family and colleagues a huge secret; he was one of the lucky 18 UK Millionaire Raffle winners. The retail worker from Sheffield 41 grinned and said “I was tempted to say it to people but then I thought ''i''ll keep quiet for now, until I know what''s happening''”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“I''d be walking down the street or sat on a bus when a big smile would come across my face and I''d think ''I''m a millionaire''”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“I think i''ll have this smile on my face for the rest of my life”</p>\r\n<img style="padding:5px; padding-bottom:30px;" src="http://www.euromillions.com/images/3478966623.jpg" alt="Euromillions Winner" width="215" height="152" align="right" />\r\n<p>The amateur astronomer who is 41 and living with his parents is planning to buy a detached house in the quiet part of the city and has already bought himself a new telescope. Despite his huge win Paul plans to stay working on at Waitrose part time as he loves his jobs selling electricals. Paul is a regular lottery player who bought extra tickets in anticipation of the 18 winners being created in the millionaire raffle on the 25th November. We wonder if he''s going to take the same preparations for the 25 guaranteed millionaire draws on the 23rd December.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Lottery winners assemble for charity</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>In Scotland today 9 lotto millionaires got together yesterday to bring an early Christmas to a group of terminally ill children. A large red double floored bus was transformed into a children''s Christmas grotto, in which the generous winners delivered gifts to Robin House, a children''s hospice in Balloch, Scotland.</p>\r\n\r\n<img style="padding:5px;" src="http://www.euromillions.com/images/winbus.jpg" alt="Euromillions Winners" align="left"  />\r\n\r\n<p>The winners included Christine Weir who won €161 million on the Euromillions earlier this year. Also Charlie and Geraldine Hilling from Cumbernauld who won €3 million in 2005 commented “We clubbed together to gift some items that the hospice had on a Christmas wish-list to bring some extra cheer to the children.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lottery winners come in all shapes and sizes but in the case of today we see that they can be both the most humble and generous people any of us could hope to meet!</p>', 'Secret Millionaire and The Generous Winners', 'Millionaire Raffle, Euromillions Winners', 'With the jackpot back to basics today we discover the UK''s latest millionaire and observe the generosity of past winners', 2, 1323190035, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'secret millionaire Christmas gifts', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323172897, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (38, 28, 'en', 'latest_euromillions_winners_tuesday_december_6th', 'Latest Euromillions Winners Tuesday December 6th', '<p>Last night saw another Euromillions rollover with no winner of the jackpot with their 7 matching numbers. The last time a rollover began it was quickly grabbed up by a French winner while the prize was still in it''s infancy! Many Euromillions players -and game organisers- will be hoping to see it build up and push into the high jackpot amounts seen in the past, giving somebody a possibly massive Christmas present.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite the jackpot from last night remaining unclaimed the winning numbers 19, 20, 21, 34, 38 with lucky stars 3 and 9 still made plenty of people much better off!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Big smiles will no doubt be on the faces of 4 prize winners who have matched 5 numbers and 1 Lucky Star to land themselves a handsome €247,025 each. We''re also fairly sure that another 4 winners of €82,342 won''t be unhappy at the 5 main numbers they successfully matched.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In fact a total of 1931 people won a prize of over €100, and an enormous 1,640,871 won some sort of cash prize of more value than the ticket price.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Euromillions jackpot prize may be the dream of many, but for so many more the aim is to make profit on their ticket cost as often as possible, and to that end the Euromillions delivers!</p>', 'Latest Euromillions Winners Tuesday 6th December', 'Euromillions Winners, Euromillions Results', 'No jackpot winner from Tuesday''s draw, but plenty of cash prizes won, find out more here', 2, 1323272255, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Latest Euromillions Results News December 6th', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323272255, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (39, 29, 'es', 'proximo_sorteo_viernes_9_de_diciembre_de_2011', 'Próximo Sorteo Viernes 9 de diciembre de 2011', '<p>El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar el viernes 9 de diciembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego el bote de 26 millones de euros. Hubo solamente una renovación el martes 2 de diciembre pasado que hizo pasar la suma del bote de 15 millones de euros a 26 millones de euros. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> Este viernes a las 21h30 tendrá lugar el sorteo en Paris, ¿que va a pasar en este sorteo? ¿Será ganado el bote otra vez a su comienzo o se renovará para crecer y acercarse de navidad con un premio más y más importante? Respuesta mañana a la noche. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Euromillions.com les desea buena suerte a todos en sus apuestas.</p>', 'Próximo Sorteo Viernes 9 de diciembre de 2011', 'euromillones, euromillions, sorteo, bote,', 'El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar el viernes 9 de diciembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego el bote de 26 millones de euros.', 2, 1323350877, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Sorteo-9-diciembre-2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323350877, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (40, 30, 'es', 'yahoo_gana_a_estafadores_de_loteria_por_e_mail', 'Yahoo gana a estafadores de lotería por e-mail', '<p>Estafadores de lotería por Internet recibieron su sentencia; USD 610 millones (€454 Millones). Esta es la increíble suma que los estafadores tienen que pagar a Yahoo después de haber hecho mal uso de la marca mandando correos electrónicos a millones de personas diciéndoles que habían ganado la lotería.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Los correos electrónicos que fueron mandados eran por supuesto falsos y diseñados con el fin de que usuarios desprevenidos darían datos personales o bancarios para recibir el premio, pero la idea era únicamente robar los datos de las cuentas bancarias.\r\n\r\n<p> En algunos casos las víctimas mandan directamente dinero a los estafadores para cubrir los supuestamente honorarios de procesamiento o gastos de envío de los premios imaginarios. Esto demuestra la evolución que las estafas de lotería tienen más y más tendencia a realizarse por correo electrónico y la facilidad para la gente de caer en este tipo de trampas. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> Los actores de la estafa fueron condenados el lunes pasado por un juez federal y gracias a los registros de Internet la compañía pudo identificarlos como siendo Nigerianos y Tailandeses. Yahoo afirma que entre diciembre del 2006 y mayo del 2009 más de 11,6 millones de correos con la estafa fueron mandados a través de su servicio de correo. La corte concedió, por ser víctima de violación a la ley ‘Can-Spam Act’, 50 dólares por correo fraudulento a Yahoo, lo que da un total de 585 millones de dólares. La ley ‘Can-Spam Act’ regula los correos recibidos pero no solicitados.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Yahoo está consciente de que va a ser difícil colectar la suma ya que Nigeria está conocido como un ‘paraíso’ para los timos por correo electrónico y que los estafadores de este tipo nunca aparecen. Hasta ahora es exactamente lo que está pasando y es justamente lo que da miedo a Yahoo ya que la suma es excesiva y que representa la mitad de las ganancias de Yahoo en el año 2010. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> La corte ha claramente ido a favor de Yahoo, sin embargo, la juez Laura Taylor Swain expresó sus dudas acerca de que Yahoo podría colectar una parte del dinero que les deben los estafadores. La juez escribió:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>"Los acusados nunca han respondido en esta acción o han comparecidos ante el tribunal, y mucho menos colaboraron con el tribunal." </p>\r\n\r\n<p> Para obtener más información acerca de los timos por correo electrónico y cómo evitarlos lean nuestra página de <a href="http://euromillions.com/es/timo-de-loterias-por-mail" title="Timo de loterías por mail y cómo evitarlos">timo de loterías por correo electrónico</a>. </p>', 'Yahoo gana a estafadores de lotería por e-mail', 'euromillones, yahoo, timo, loteria, mail,', 'Los timos de lotería por e-mail son muy comunes y muchos perdieron dinero. Estafadores perdieron frente a Yahoo y tienen que pagar €450 millones. Leer más...', 2, 1323691023, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Yahoo wins court case', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323690975, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (41, 31, 'es', 'proximo_sorteo_martes_13_de_diciembre_de_2011', 'Próximo Sorteo: Martes 13 de diciembre de 2011', '<p>El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar este martes 13 de diciembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego la suma de 33 millones de euros. En el último sorteo Euromillones que ponía en juego el bote de 26 millones de euros nadie coincidió con la combinación ganadora del sorteo así que la suma del bote se renueva en el sorteo de este martes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Si el bote sigue creciendo habrá euphoria en la navidad. En efecto, quedan 4 sorteos antes de navidad y si nadie se lleva el bote durante estos sorteos se estima que la suma del bote alcanzará 100 millones de euros. Por supuesto, la lotería Euromillones sigue su actividad durante las fiestas y el bote tiene para renovarse hasta 190 millones de euros. La única manera de saber que va a pasar con el bote es comprobar los resultados de los sorteos a medida de que ocurran.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://euromillions.com/es" title="Inicio Euromillions.com">Euromillions.com</a> desea buena suerte a todos los participantes Euromillones.</p>', 'Próximo Sorteo: Martes 13 de diciembre de 2011', 'euromillones, euromillions, sorteo, bote,', 'El próximo sorteo Euromillones tendrá lugar este martes 13 de septiembre de 2011 y pondrá en juego la suma de 33 millones de euros.', 2, 1325256567, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Sorteo-13-diciembre-2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323693174, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (42, 30, 'en', 'yahoo_beats_email_lottery_scammers', 'Yahoo Beats Email Lottery Scammers', '<p>Internet lottery conmen are being ordered to pay out an enormous $610 million (€454 million) to Yahoo, after running a fraudulent campaign in which they emailed millions of people to tell them they had won the lottery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The emails they sent were of course bogus and designed to have unsuspecting users hand over personal details to receive their prize, but instead their bank accounts would be stolen from.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In some cases the victims even sent money directly to the scam artists to cover apparent processing fees or as postal charges for imaginary prizes. This highlights the growing trend in lottery email scams and how easily so many people can run foul of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yahoo lead the proceedings in court to take these scammers to task over the fraudulent activity, after they used Yahoo''s name and brand to lure users into a false sense of security. This is not only a case of trademark infringement, as US law on sending junk mail strictly prohibits these actions also.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Legal action began in 2008 when Yahoo suspected that foreign individuals and companies had sent over 12 million emails using their trademark, telling people they had won lottery prize. After 3 years of proceedings the courts have ordered the crooks to pay $27 million (€20 million) to Yahoo for trademark infringement and $583 million (€434 million) for breaking US law.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The judge''s decision was spelled out clearly in writing when he said that Yahoo''s allegations were “uncontroverted”, there can be no doubt over the guilt of the scammers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The court case has clearly gone in Yahoo''s favour however a US Judge Laura Taylor Swain expressed her doubts that Yahoo would collect any of the money owed to them by the scammers, she wrote:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“Defendants have never responded in this action, or appeared before the court, much less co-operated with the court”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just click for more information on how to protect yourself from <a href="http://www.euromillions.com/lottery-email-scams/">lottery email scams</a></p>', 'Yahoo Beats Email Lottery Scammers', 'Lottery Email, Lottery Fraud, Lottery scam, Yahoo', 'Courts take the side of Yahoo in massive case and order big damages to be paid', 2, 1323765749, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Yahoo wins court case', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323698905, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (43, 32, 'en', 'friday_rollover_and_online_winner', 'Friday Rollover And Online Winner', '<p>Friday''s Euromillion Result saw the third rollover so it looks like the prize amounts might be about to grow into the truly enormous jackpots we''ve seen in the past! Despite the lack of a jackpot winner there were still plenty of people made rich from Friday''s draw of 12, 21, 29, 44, 47 and Lucky Stars 1 and 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 people beat the odds to win the second prize amount of €295,613 by matching 5 of their main numbers and 1 Lucky Star. Double that amount of people matched 5 main numbers on their own to win €49,269. Ideally we can still have plenty of big cash winners while the jackpot rolls over into the hundreds of millions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In other Euromillions news a mystery man has come forward in Belfast to claim over €1 million, won with his UK Millionaire Month Raffle ticket. The lucky player opted to play his Euromillions entry online and thus never actually touched his ticket.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The man who has chosen to reveal himself only as Mr T would naturally like to remain anonymous but did have this to say, “I''m a quiet and shy person”, “I don''t want any attention”. However a friend of the new millionaire was quoted saying “I''m so pleased for him”, “I''m happy to see him do well, because he is a lovely guy”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>National Lottery spokesman said well done to Mr T, “He has banked this amazing prize with just a few simple clicks – he didn''t even have to pick up a ticket!”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>“If you play interactively we not only check your numbers, but also let you know when you have won -it couldn''t be simpler”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr T is yet another Millionaires Month winner to come forward but there will be plenty more before Christmas day. Just click for more information on the <a href="http://www.euromillions.com/millionaire-month/">Millionaires Month</a></p>', 'Friday Rollover and Online Winner', 'Euromillions Rollover, Euromillions Online, Euromillions Winner', 'The third consecutive rollover heralds a possibly huge Christmas jackpot, while another player wins millions after buying their ticket online', 2, 1324464693, 11, 'Rory Renehan', 'Friday 9th December Rollover', '', NULL, 'Lottery News December', NULL, 1323701301, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (44, 26, 'de', 'euromillions_jackpot_gewann_in_frankreich', 'Euromillions Jackpot gewann in Frankreich', '<p>Für die Auslosung am 2. Dezember gibt es einen glücklichen Gewinner, der den Jackpot von 27.094.319 € knackte. Bis jetzt hat sich der Gewinner noch nicht gemeldet, doch wir glauben nicht, dass es noch lange dauernd wird, bis derjenige sich  zu seinem wohlverdienten Gewinn bei la Francaise de Jeux (FDJ) meldet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Gewinnzahlen waren 27, 40, 7, 43 und 30, mit den Glückszahlen 8 und 9. Das Gewinnerlos wurde in einer Tabak-Abteilung eines Geschäftes in Côte-d''Or verkauft. Aus Gründen der Sicherheit zögert die FDJ den genauen Standort des Ladens bekanntzugeben.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In dieser Situation kann man nicht sagen, ob der Gewinner aus der Côte-d''Or kommt oder ein Gewinner ausländischer Herkunft, der einfach nur zu Besuch war, als er das Los kaufte. In jedem Fall appelliert die FDJ an jeden, der in der Nähe ein Los gekauft hat, es genau zu überprüfen, um sicherzustellen, dass der Gewinner sich bald meldet.</p>', 'Euromillions Jackpot gewann in Frankreich', 'Euromillions, Gewinn, Frankreich', 'Für die Auslosung am 2. Dezember gibt es einen glücklichen Gewinner, der den Jackpot von 27.094.319 € knackte', 1, 1323076545, 9, 'Jenny Zimmerman', 'Jackpot Won In France December 2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323767705, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `news_details` VALUES (45, 33, 'es', 'sorteo_13_de_diciembre_de_2011', 'Sorteo 13 de diciembre de 2011', '<p> El sorteo del martes 13 de diciembre de 2011 proponía un bote de 33 millones de euros y no ha sido ganado por ningún participante. La combinación ganadora del sorteo del 13 de diciembre es 07 - 12 - 18 - 33 - 37 / 1 - 11. Para el bote, se trata entonces de una renovación; la cuarta renovación seguida desde el sorteo del 06 de diciembre.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p> El próximo sorteo euromillones tendrá lugar este viernes 16 de diciembre y pondrá en juego, además de los otros premios, el bote de 46 millones de euros. </p>', 'Sorteo 13 de diciembre de 2011', 'euromillones, euromillions, resultado, sorteo, bote,', 'El sorteo del martes 13 de diciembre de 2011 proponía un bote de 33 millones de euros y no ha sido ganado por ningún participante.', 2, 1323882540, 10, 'Michael Hermes', 'Sorteo-anterior-13-diciembre', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1323882540, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
